---
import challengesImage from "../../../public/images/home/challenges/man-with-laptop.jpg";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
---

<section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container space-y-4">
    <h2
      class="text-primary text-3xl leading-tight font-bold uppercase lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl"
    >
      WE UNDERSTAND THE CHALLENGES YOU'RE FACING
    </h2>

    <!-- Paragraph -->
    <p class="max-w-[1000px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      We understand that attracting new residents to your senior living facility
      can be a challenge. With rising competition and high marketing costs,
      filling vacancies can feel like an uphill battle.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto mt-16 px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Left Column - Text Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Main Heading -->

        <!-- Sub-heading -->
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 uppercase lg:text-4xl">
          YOU MIGHT BE STRUGGLING WITH:
        </h3>

        <!-- Bulleted List -->
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-lg">
            <div class="bg-primary h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Inefficient marketing strategies</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-lg">
            <div class="bg-primary h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700"
              >Wasting budget on unqualified leads</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-lg">
            <div class="bg-primary h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700"
              >Difficulty in differentiating from other local facilities</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-lg">
            <div class="bg-primary h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
            <span class="text-gray-700"
              >Relying on expensive traditional methods with low returns</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Image Content -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div
          class="relative max-w-[650px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        >
          <!-- Placeholder Image -->
          <Image
            src={challengesImage}
            alt="Business professional looking stressed while working on laptop"
            class="h-auto w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />

          <!-- Image Overlay for better text contrast if needed -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Proven Method Section -->
  <div class="container mx-auto mt-20 px-4">
    <div class="mx-auto">
      <!-- Main Heading -->
      <h2
        class="text-primary mb-12 text-3xl leading-tight font-bold uppercase lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl"
      >
        OUR PROVEN METHOD DELIVERS RESULTS
      </h2>

      <!-- Bullet Points in Boxes -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div
          class="flex items-start space-x-4 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4"
        >
          <div class="bg-primary mt-2 h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We provide a unique, cost-effective marketing solution that
            guarantees new resident placements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex items-start space-x-4 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4"
        >
          <div class="bg-primary mt-2 h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Our targeted advertising strategy ensures your marketing budget is
            used efficiently, reaching only families actively looking for senior
            living options.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex items-start space-x-4 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4"
        >
          <div class="bg-primary mt-2 h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We work exclusively with one facility per area, so we focus entirely
            on your success.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex items-start space-x-4 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4"
        >
          <div class="bg-primary mt-2 h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            With our proven method, you'll attract 2-5 new residents each month
            at a cost lower than what it typically takes to place a single
            resident.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Ensure proper spacing on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .space-y-8 > * + * {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
